      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific will continue\nthe Sunday excursions to st. Maries.\nFerrells ana St. Joe during the sum-\nmer. Train will leave Spokane s n.\nm. for Occur dAlene. Steamer Cakes\nleaving there on arrival of train for\nu delightful ride across the lake and\nup the st. Joe river, arriving ut Fer\nrells about p. m, where stop of\n80 minutes will be made for dinner.\nThose preferring to do so can take\nlunch baskets and eat lunch on the\nboat. Returning train will arrive\nSpokane about p. m. Fare for the\nround trip 50.\n\n\nJ. w. HILL, Gen. Agt."
    }
